+// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0
+/*
+ * Rockchip Video Decoder VP9 backend
+ *
+ * Copyright (C) 2019 Collabora, Ltd.
+ *	Boris Brezillon <boris.brezillon@collabora.com>
